STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Carlos SIERRA-ROJAS, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0492 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Carlos Sierra-Rojas appeals from his conviction and sentence for harboring a runaway. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
